text.title: UITGEZEILD.
text.p: HELLEVOETSLUIS, 15 Sept., W.Z.W.; Feijenoord, S., Londen. - Vartry, S., Dublin. - Bradford, S , Grimsby. - Cycloop, S., Middell. Zee, via Brouwershaven. — Gisteren nog: Seagull, S., Huil. BRIELLE, 14 Sept., W. Z.W.; Avalon, S., Harwich. — 15 Sept.; Edith, Huil. - Annie, S., Goole. ZOLTKAMP, 13 Sept.; Marie, Rasmussen, Avontuur. BREMERHAVEN, 13 Sept.; Jantina Petronella, de Boer, Flensburg. DANTZIG, 12 Sept ;Nina, S, Amst. KROONSTAD, 10 Sept.; Elise Maria, Petersen, Hoorn. FALMOUTH, 12 Sept.; Divitz, Gronow, Koogerpolder.- Bandina Elisabeth, de Jonge, Buenos Ayres n. Shilloth. - Ligure, Sirnmonetta, Schiedam. — 13 Sept.; Clasina, Sannes, Rio Grande n. Belfast. QUEENSTOWN, 14 Sept.; Wild Wave, Bevan, Iquique n. Amst. RÜNCORN, 13 Sept.; Arm & Elisabeth, Toms, Dordrecht. STOCKTON, 13 Sept.; de Hoop, Pott, Christiania. LIVERPOOL, 13 Sept.; Gannet, S., Rott.' GRIMSBY, 13 Sept.; Ceres, de Boer, Elseneur. MIDDLESBRO, 13 Sept.; Richard & Emilie, Boothly, Zwolle. SUNDERLAND, 13 Sept.; Choice, Hardcastle, Rott. - Heron, Lawson, Nieuwediep. REDON, 4 Sept.; Jumeaux, Bego, Rott. . LISSABON, sSept.; Clémence,Bauwens,Villanora.-Dankbaarheid, v. d. Berg, Gibraltar. NEW-YORK, 3 Sept.; zeilkl.: Johanna Maria, Post, Buenos-Ayres. PHILADELPHIA, 31 Aug.; zeilkl.; Halfden, Sorby, Rott.
